      "title": "Navy lends helping hand to devotees engaged in \u2018Paada Yaathra\u2019",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Navy, as it has been the practice, is lending its helping hand to devotees who are engaged in foot pilgrimage, known as \u2018Paada Yaathra\u2019 along the route from the entrance of Kumana National Park to Kumbukkan Oya. The traditional foot pilgrimage marches from Jaffna to Sella Kataragama annually, with the participation of many devotees."
      ],
